    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Available for the discerning driver is this E46-generation M3, a mechanically robust example of the legendary S54-powered platform. This 3.2L high-revving inline-six features individual throttle bodies and a dual-VANOS system that has been recently overhauled for optimal cam timing. Power is managed via a Getrag 420G six-speed manual transmission, delivering torque through a variable M-differential. The chassis has been addressed with essential subframe reinforcement plates and the suspension utilizes refreshed bushings paired with Bilstein dampers for precise turn-in. While showing minor cosmetic wear consistent with its 'good' status, the drivetrain remains tight with no rod bearing noise and a linear power band up to the 8,000 RPM redline. A purist\u2019s spec focused on mechanical longevity and tactile feedback.",
